Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.82,0:01:33.41,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}So, what do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.58,0:01:37.08,Ep_Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1023,1)}Episode 2: Meeting the Goblins
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.41,0:01:34.38,Main,Veldora,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.89,0:01:37.71,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}About the Unlimited Imprisonment \Nseal that hero put on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.71,0:01:42.29,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I feel bad knowing my friend's \Nbeen sealed here for 300 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.36,0:01:44.40,Main,Veldora,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.36,0:01:47.83,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give me those puppy dog eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.83,0:01:50.80,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be one thing coming from \Na cute girl, but a dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.21,0:01:54.24,Main,Veldora,0000,0000,0000,,If you have a way to get \Nme out, I'd appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.69,0:01:56.55,Main,Veldora,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The thing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.55,0:02:01.43,Main,Veldora,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't have lasted another 100 \Nyears before my magic ran out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.43,0:02:03.65,Main,Veldora,0000,0000,0000,,I keep losing more and more magicules...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.25,0:02:06.65,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why this cave \Nis so rich in magicules,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.85,0:02:09.77,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,and there are so many \Nvaluable herbs and ore.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.27,0:02:13.40,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,What happens when your magic runs out?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.40,0:02:15.01,Main,Veldora,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a huge deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.01,0:02:16.54,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,It's not?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.13,0:02:20.29,Main,Veldora,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just die, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.72,0:02:22.48,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I... I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.22,0:02:27.39,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,After all these years of \Nisolation, you just die, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.82,0:02:30.30,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Might as well try this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.00,0:02:37.25,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Great Sage, use Predator to consume \Nthe Unlimited Imprisonment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.53,0:02:43.88,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,Failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.88,0:02:46.11,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it won't be that easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.70,0:02:49.11,Main,Veldora,0000,0000,0000,,See? It's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.24,0:02:52.30,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there anything we can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.30,0:02:54.37,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,Examining the possibilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.54,0:02:58.31,Main,Veldora,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't just keep \Ntalking to your own skill!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.31,0:02:59.41,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Old man...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.75,0:03:01.83,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,Examination completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.31,0:03:04.00,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,Possibilities include...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.88,0:03:06.09,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.77,0:03:08.37,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I see, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.73,0:03:11.59,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,It's only a possibility, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.64,0:03:15.72,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,She says if we can analyze the Unlimited \NImprisonment from both inside and out,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.72,0:03:17.50,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,we might be able to remove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.50,0:03:18.94,Main,Veldora,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.94,0:03:21.60,Main,Veldora,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, but... I can't analyze \Nit from the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.03,0:03:25.61,Main,Veldora,0000,0000,0000,,My skills are sealed along with me, \Nso I can't use them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.74,0:03:28.98,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,If you can just give me the data, \NI can analyze it out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.64,0:03:32.51,Main,Veldora,0000,0000,0000,,But that could take some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.51,0:03:35.17,Main,Veldora,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you want to \Nstay in here that long?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.17,0:03:38.33,Main,Veldora,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, not that I mind, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.33,0:03:39.70,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Good point...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.70,0:03:43.22,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Since I'm here, I'd like to search \Nfor others from my homeland.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.03,0:03:44.93,Main,Veldora,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.81,0:03:47.25,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,So here's a suggestion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.34,0:03:49.76,Main,Veldora,0000,0000,0000,,A suggestion?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.26,0:03:53.51,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Want to get in my stomach?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.64,0:04:07.31,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use my skills, Great Sage and Predator, \Nto analyze Unlimited Imprisonment
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.31,0:04:09.82,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,while you try to destroy it from the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.13,0:04:13.87,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be quarantined in my\Nstomach, so you won't disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.46,0:04:15.32,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.96,0:04:30.04,Main,Veldora,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds interesting! Please, do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.04,0:04:32.72,Main,Veldora,0000,0000,0000,,I'll entrust my entirety to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.92,0:04:35.63,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you want to \Nbelieve me that easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.82,0:04:37.17,Main,Veldora,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.17,0:04:40.07,Main,Veldora,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds more fun to break through \NUnlimited Imprisonment together
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.07,0:04:43.31,Main,Veldora,0000,0000,0000,,than to wait here alone until you come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.92,0:04:45.05,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.05,0:04:47.50,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Better two than one...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.95,0:04:49.32,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds great!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.53,0:04:50.56,Main,Veldora,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.25,0:04:55.17,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay, I'll use Predator to—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.17,0:04:56.75,Main,Veldora,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.13,0:05:01.43,Main,Veldora,0000,0000,0000,,Before we start, I'll give you a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.93,0:05:04.16,Main,Veldora,0000,0000,0000,,You can give me one, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.16,0:05:05.08,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.50,0:05:08.92,Main,Veldora,0000,0000,0000,,It will engrave onto our souls \Nthe fact that we are equals.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.92,0:05:12.10,Main,Veldora,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be what humans call a "family name,"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.10,0:05:15.09,Main,Veldora,0000,0000,0000,,but the name I give you will \Ngrant you divine protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.59,0:05:20.13,Main,Veldora,0000,0000,0000,,You are still nameless, so you'll\Nbecome a monster with a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.02,0:05:22.73,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,A monster with a name, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.73,0:05:23.85,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds good!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.22,0:05:25.40,Main,Veldora,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.01,0:05:27.88,Main,Veldora,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a cool name!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.88,0:05:29.10,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Same to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.85,0:05:31.65,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,A cool name...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.65,0:05:33.16,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.16,0:05:35.51,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,The Storm Dragon, Veldora...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.90,0:05:37.65,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Storm, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.05,0:05:41.91,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,And... what's another \Nword for a storm, again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.13,0:05:44.54,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Storm... sounds kinda weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.96,0:05:46.79,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Tempest!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.51,0:05:50.33,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think of "Tempest"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.86,0:05:51.97,Main,Veldora,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.97,0:05:54.09,Main,Veldora,0000,0000,0000,,Tempest, you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.09,0:05:56.05,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.34,0:05:58.66,Main,Veldora,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds fantastic!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.66,0:06:02.22,Main,Veldora,0000,0000,0000,,As of today, I am Veldora Tempest!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.27,0:06:05.35,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You {\i1}like{\i0} it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.66,0:06:09.63,Main,Veldora,0000,0000,0000,,And I will grant you the name "Rimuru."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.63,0:06:10.90,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Rimuru...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.90,0:06:12.36,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.81,0:06:15.36,Main,Veldora,0000,0000,0000,,You will be Rimuru Tempest!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.85,0:06:23.91,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,At that moment, something \Nchanged deep in my soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.74,0:06:28.91,sign_9225_96_Rimuru_Tempest,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(1030,1)}Rimuru Tempest
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.29,0:06:28.91,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,The name "Rimuru Tempest" \Nhad become engraved upon it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.54,0:06:33.17,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I am... Rimuru Tempest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.85,0:06:34.92,Main,Veldora,0000,0000,0000,,Rimuru...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.47,0:06:37.24,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Veldora Tempest...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.00,0:06:43.73,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'm going to eat you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.73,0:06:46.68,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Break out of that \NUnlimited Imprisonment already!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.05,0:06:49.38,Main,Veldora,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.38,0:06:52.19,Main,Veldora,0000,0000,0000,,I will see you face-to-face in no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.41,0:06:53.31,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.85,0:06:55.94,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Unique skill: Predator!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.91,0:07:12.85,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,That ended far too soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.41,0:07:15.67,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I was just talking with him a moment ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.67,0:07:19.67,sign_10446_109_Unlimited_Impris,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Unlimited Imprisonment
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.31,0:07:19.67,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to analyze the unique \Nskill Unlimited Imprisonment?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.35,0:07:22.40,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Please do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.50,0:07:26.58,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,A great tremor rocked the world on this day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.02,0:07:29.51,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,The disappearance of the \NStorm Dragon Veldora,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.51,0:07:31.96,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,a Catastrophe-class monster, was confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.69,0:07:37.91,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,The cave where Veldora had been sealed \Nwas in the Great Forest of Jura.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.41,0:07:42.70,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,In the area of the Great Forest \Nof Jura are several countries.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.19,0:07:40.69,sign_11010_116_Barren_Lands_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz313}Barren Lands
