Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.69,0:07:42.70,sign_11046_120_Kingdom_of_Falmu,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Kingdom of Falmus
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.69,0:07:42.70,sign_11046_121_Kingdom_of_Blumu,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Kingdom of Blumund
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.69,0:07:42.70,sign_11046_122_Sealed_Cave,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Sealed Cave
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.69,0:07:42.70,sign_11046_123_Lake_Siss_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Lake Siss
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.35,0:07:49.94,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,In one of them, the Kingdom of Blumund...
