Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.50,0:07:55.38,sign_11329_129_Minister_Baron_V,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(524,521)}Minister {\fs24}Baron Veryard
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.57,0:07:56.13,Main,Veryard,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You've heard about the \NStorm Dragon Veldora, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.56,0:07:58.23,Main,Fuze,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.63,0:08:01.13,sign_11329_129_Minister_Baron_V,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(524,474)}Guild Master {\fs24}Fuze
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.22,0:08:02.38,Main,Veryard,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I should have expected \Nas much of a guild master.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.93,0:08:06.77,Main,Veryard,0000,0000,0000,,So, can you tell me what measures \Nthe guild intends to take?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.27,0:08:09.89,Main,Fuze,0000,0000,0000,,We have no plans to take \Nany particular action.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.25,0:08:15.15,Main,Veryard,0000,0000,0000,,The disappearance of Veldora is predicted \Nto galvanize the monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.93,0:08:22.20,Main,Fuze,0000,0000,0000,,There is a chance that the Eastern\NKingdom will advance through the
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.20,0:08:25.16,Main,Fuze,0000,0000,0000,,previously impassable region that \Nthe Storm Dragon was sealed in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.58,0:08:27.40,Main,Veryard,0000,0000,0000,,If they get through that forest,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.40,0:08:29.66,Main,Veryard,0000,0000,0000,,the provinces surrounding \Nthe Great Forest of Jura
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.03,0:08:33.41,Main,Veryard,0000,0000,0000,,will fall under the empire's \Nrule, in the blink of an eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.23,0:08:41.17,Main,Fuze,0000,0000,0000,,You look tired. \NAre you getting enough sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.14,0:08:46.10,Main,Fuze,0000,0000,0000,,As a favor to an old friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.10,0:08:48.71,Main,Fuze,0000,0000,0000,,I'll conduct an investigation personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.71,0:08:52.68,Main,Fuze,0000,0000,0000,,I'll look into the state of the Great Forest \Nof Jura and the kingdom's movements.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.25,0:08:55.19,Main,Veryard,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. Please see to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.47,0:09:03.08,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,The chaos in the surrounding \Ncountries since noticing
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.08,0:09:06.40,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,that Veldora disappeared was \Nlike a disturbed hornet's nest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.82,0:09:09.64,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, Rimuru had no way to know this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.23,0:09:13.58,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,How many days has it been \Nsince I ate Veldora?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.93,0:09:17.47,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I wandered around everywhere, \Ntrying to get out of the cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.02,0:09:20.53,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I gobbled up all the herbs \Nand ores I came across
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.53,0:09:22.59,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,to store them in my body.
