Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.72,0:09:52.83,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I tried out lots of things \Nand gained some new skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.51,0:09:56.08,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,And then... I found the one!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.49,0:09:59.55,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,The one bound to me by \Nthe red thread of fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.55,0:10:00.58,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Except it wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.58,0:10:03.09,sign_14400_175_Black_Serpent_Ap,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Black Serpent Appeared
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.96,0:10:06.83,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,This looks bad. \NI doubt it's gonna let me escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.63,0:10:12.72,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,But wait... This is nothing \Ncompared to Veldora, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.66,0:10:15.85,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's not as scary as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.14,0:10:17.06,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.81,0:10:21.98,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Water Blade!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.01,0:10:30.66,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,That's a much stronger \Ntechnique than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.37,0:10:33.58,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to be careful who I use it on...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.42,0:10:35.60,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.01,0:10:39.72,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,If I use Predator to eat \Nthis snake and analyze it,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.72,0:10:42.92,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,wouldn't I be able to take its abilities?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.08,0:10:46.34,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Right! Eat it whole!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.94,0:10:55.40,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Blech!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.40,0:10:58.10,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I can't taste things, but still! Blech!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.02,0:11:00.31,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,Analysis complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.68,0:11:04.51,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,Skills: Poisonous Breath and \NSense Heat Source acquired.
