Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.31,0:11:04.31,sign_15858_193_Sense_Heat_Sourc,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,888)}Sense\NHeat Source\N{\fs16}Acquired
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.95,0:11:07.57,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,You can now mimic Black Serpent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.98,0:11:07.57,sign_4961_43_It_hurts,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(820,1)}You can now mimic Black Serpent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.60,0:11:11.77,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,So I can breathe poison \Nand sense heat sources?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.77,0:11:13.91,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,That could come in pretty handy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.09,0:11:16.79,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Man, Predator sure is useful!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.45,0:11:20.30,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I'm gonna \Nacquire a lot more skills!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.96,0:11:23.33,sign_16327_201_Armorsaurus_Appe,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,138)}Armorsaurus Appeared
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.34,0:11:29.84,sign_16480_202_Mimic_Black_Serp,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(148,1)}Mimic Black Serpent
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.34,0:11:33.05,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.34,0:11:34.05,sign_16480_202_Mimic_Black_Serp,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,245)}— Poisonous Breath —
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.94,0:11:45.19,sign_16854_205__Body_Armor__Acq,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(522,1)}"Body Armor" Acquired
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.96,0:11:45.19,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I'd better not use Poisonous \NBreath anymore...
