Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.49,0:11:57.49,sign_16854_205__Body_Armor__Acq,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(475,275)\fad(276,1)}"Paralysis Breath" Acquired
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.49,0:11:59.58,sign_16989_207_Evil_Centipede_A,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(464,66)\an8}Black Spider Appeared
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.58,0:12:01.20,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Water Blade! Water Blade! \NWater Blade! Water Blade!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.58,0:12:05.08,sign_17325_211__Sticky_Thread__,Text,0000,0000,0000,,"Sticky Thread," and  "Steel Thread" Acquired
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.30,0:12:16.55,sign_17606_212_Giant_Bat_Appear,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Giant Bat Appeared
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.31,0:12:19.81,sign_17702_213__Drain__Ultrason,Text,0000,0000,0000,,"Drain," and "Ultrasonic Wave" Acquired
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.32,0:12:22.84,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}A red water strider, A-I-U-E-O!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.84,0:12:25.53,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Little shrimp swim in the algae!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.97,0:12:27.06,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Using the organ that the bat \Nused for its Ultrasonic Wave,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.28,0:12:29.03,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I was finally able to speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.03,0:12:32.57,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,We are aliens.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.52,0:12:44.88,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Then, after several weeks of \Nwandering around that cave...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.42,0:12:46.34,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,At last...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.86,0:12:52.96,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,This is probably the exit, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.82,0:12:55.55,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Well, now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.55,0:12:57.95,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Can I cut it up with Water Blade?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.73,0:13:18.75,Main,Gido,0000,0000,0000,,It finally opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.75,0:13:21.95,Main,Gido,0000,0000,0000,,It's so rusty, the keyhole's falling apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.12,0:13:23.67,Main,Kaval,0000,0000,0000,,That's no surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.67,0:13:26.75,Main,Kaval,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody's come in here for 300 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.75,0:13:29.25,Main,Eren,0000,0000,0000,,We won't be attacked out of nowhere, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.21,0:13:34.51,Main,Eren,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, if it comes to it, \Nwe can always use Escape...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.13,0:13:38.05,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,The first humans I've seen...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.05,0:13:42.01,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what they're here for, \Nbut I guess they're adventurers?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.40,0:13:44.27,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, I can understand them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.27,0:13:51.02,sign_19763_233_Intention,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Intention
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.27,0:13:51.02,sign_19763_234_Magic_Sense_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Sense
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.27,0:13:51.02,sign_19763_235_The_use_of_Magic,Text,0000,0000,0000,,The use of Magic Sense turns sound waves \Nthat carry intention into comprehensible words.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.54,0:13:45.52,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,Answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.52,0:13:51.02,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,The use of Magic Sense turns sound waves \Nthat carry intention into comprehensible words.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.33,0:13:53.44,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why. Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.44,0:13:55.91,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I was never good at English.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.91,0:13:59.29,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,And by producing sound waves that \Ncarry your thoughts, you can converse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.29,0:14:00.55,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.03,0:14:03.54,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm a slime now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.72,0:14:07.04,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,It would suck if I talked to them \Nand they immediately attacked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.32,0:14:10.29,Main,Gido,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'm gonna \Nactivate my Stealth Arts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.34,0:14:24.84,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,He called that skill "Stealth"? \NYou could peep all you wanted with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.84,0:14:26.36,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,What a disgraceful creep!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.36,0:14:28.60,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to make friends with him later!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.99,0:14:32.89,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Are they gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.82,0:14:39.98,Main,Gido,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.98,0:14:43.06,Main,Eren,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I sensed a monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.06,0:14:44.87,Main,Eren,0000,0000,0000,,Was it my imagination?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.52,0:14:48.41,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,So I left the cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.41,0:14:51.68,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,How long has it been since \NI walked in the sunlight?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.09,0:14:54.88,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,There's been no sign of Veldora since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.16,0:14:59.47,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like he vanished for good, \Nbut I know that's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.02,0:15:02.66,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I promised, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.40,0:15:16.21,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to build up a lot of funny stories\Nto tell him about next time we meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.18,0:15:19.89,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I haven't seen the outside in so long!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.89,0:15:21.41,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,The air tastes so sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.41,0:15:22.53,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Not that I can taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.03,0:15:27.04,sign_16327_201_Armorsaurus_Appe,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(150,285)}Goblins Appeared
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.79,0:15:30.54,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Veldora...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.93,0:15:35.04,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like I'm about to have one funny \Nstory to tell you about already.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.39,0:15:37.05,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Scrawny bodies,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.26,0:15:38.80,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,beat-up weapons...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.32,0:15:44.80,Main,Leader,0000,0000,0000,,Strong one, do you have business here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.80,0:15:46.56,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Strong one?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.63,0:15:49.07,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.93,0:15:52.44,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I just need to produce sound \Nwaves carrying my thoughts?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.44,0:15:53.27,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.07,0:15:57.44,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Right, so, hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.44,0:16:01.44,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a slime, and my name is Rimuru!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.20,0:16:06.34,Main,Leader,0000,0000,0000,,We're well aware of how strong you are, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.34,0:16:09.00,Main,Leader,0000,0000,0000,,Please, quiet your voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.39,0:16:11.45,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I thought too hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.89,0:16:13.71,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,So, did you need something?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.36,0:16:16.81,Main,Leader,0000,0000,0000,,We sensed a powerful monster,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.81,0:16:18.59,Main,Leader,0000,0000,0000,,so we came here as a precaution.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.45,0:16:22.53,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I don't sense anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.53,0:16:23.80,Main,Leader,0000,0000,0000,,Surely you jest!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.80,0:16:28.01,Main,Leader,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you face us in that \Nform, we won't be fooled!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.01,0:16:29.97,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I guess he really does mean me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.48,0:16:34.85,Main,Leader,0000,0000,0000,,Strong one, having seen your \Npower, we wish to ask a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.69,0:16:40.36,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Then I was led to the Goblin Village.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.88,0:16:43.22,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,It sure is a shoddy village, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.22,0:16:45.61,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I bet Veldora could blow \Nit away with one snort.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.61,0:16:48.87,Main,Head,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome, visitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.05,0:16:52.87,Main,Head,0000,0000,0000,,I am the elder of this village.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.24,0:16:55.41,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.41,0:16:58.13,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,So, what favor did you want to ask of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.93,0:17:05.32,Main,Head,0000,0000,0000,,Have you noticed that monsters \Nhave been unusually active of late?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.32,0:17:06.38,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.38,0:17:11.87,Main,Head,0000,0000,0000,,Our god disappeared one month ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.87,0:17:17.05,Main,Head,0000,0000,0000,,As a result, monsters in the area \Nhave been continually harassing us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.05,0:17:20.26,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Their god? Does he mean Veldora?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.26,0:17:22.03,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,The timing fits.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.03,0:17:25.15,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I guess he was keeping monsters away?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.15,0:17:29.49,Main,Head,0000,0000,0000,,We tried to fight them, \Nbut we lack the numbers...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.49,0:17:31.66,Main,Leader,0000,0000,0000,,S-So we hoped you would...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.66,0:17:34.54,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,...help you out, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.54,0:17:37.06,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm just a slime.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.06,0:17:40.42,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt I can do all the \Nthings you expect of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.25,0:17:42.46,Main,Head,0000,0000,0000,,Please, don't be modest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.46,0:17:43.67,Main,Leader,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be modest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.92,0:17:48.52,Main,Head,0000,0000,0000,,A mere slime would not \Nemit such an intense aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.52,0:17:51.93,Main,Head,0000,0000,0000,,You are quite a famous monster, are you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.08,0:17:53.57,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Aura?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.57,0:17:56.75,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,What's he talking about? \NI don't have one of those.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.69,0:18:00.61,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Great Sage, change Magic Sense's perspective
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.61,0:18:02.69,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,and let me look at myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.69,0:18:04.48,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,Changing perspective.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.61,0:18:11.49,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! I've been emitting \Nan aura this whole time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.65,0:18:14.99,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I've been walking down \Na major street with my fly open!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.99,0:18:16.52,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.52,0:18:19.12,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why the Goblins were scared of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.42,0:18:23.63,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to the elder to notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.84,0:18:28.72,Main,Head,0000,0000,0000,,But of course. You cannot hide \Nthe formidable air about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.72,0:18:29.62,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.62,0:18:31.52,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,So you figured it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.52,0:18:34.49,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,You guys show a lot of potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.29,0:18:37.93,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I sucked it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.35,0:18:41.45,Main,Head,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... Have you been testing us?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.45,0:18:45.86,Main,Head,0000,0000,0000,,It's fortunate that so many of \Nus were frightened by your aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.86,0:18:47.52,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.52,0:18:50.66,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,You've got potential if you \Ncan talk to me without fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.81,0:18:52.53,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,What potential?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.53,0:18:55.99,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, how did those \Nhumans in the cave not see my aura?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.99,0:18:57.29,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Are those guys okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.46,0:18:59.47,Main,Head,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.47,0:19:02.79,Main,Head,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, as for the favor we wish to ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.09,0:19:05.95,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,According to the Goblins,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.95,0:19:10.59,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,wolf monsters, Direwolves, \Nattacked them from the east,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.02,0:19:14.10,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,and many Goblins died in the ensuing battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.04,0:19:18.93,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, Direwolves are so much \Nmore powerful than Goblins that
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.93,0:19:21.73,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,it takes ten Goblins to even have \Na chance at beating one Direwolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.33,0:19:26.44,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,And there was one warrior among them with \Na name, who served as their guardian.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.16,0:19:32.47,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Even that warrior was killed, \Nleaving the village in peril.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.18,0:19:36.45,Main,Head,0000,0000,0000,,There are about 100 Direwolves in total.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.72,0:19:39.27,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,How many do we have?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.27,0:19:43.21,Main,Head,0000,0000,0000,,Including females, we have \Nabout 60 who can fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.21,0:19:45.53,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,That's a pretty devastating \Ndifference in strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.53,0:19:47.46,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,It's like an impossible video game.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.94,0:19:52.85,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,So did that Goblin warrior fight \Nthem knowing he couldn't win?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.23,0:19:55.64,Main,Head,0000,0000,0000,,No... That warrior gave \Nhis life just retrieving
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.64,0:19:59.35,Main,Head,0000,0000,0000,,information on the Direwolves for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.57,0:20:06.58,Main,Head,0000,0000,0000,,The warrior was my son, \Nand his elder brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.27,0:20:10.44,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.44,0:20:12.27,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me for asking that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.49,0:20:19.77,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Elder, tell me one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.77,0:20:21.04,Main,Head,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.24,0:20:25.68,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,What will I get in return \Nfor helping this village?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.68,0:20:28.54,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,What can you guys give me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.59,0:20:37.04,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not actually looking for compensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.04,0:20:40.22,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I just need to put on a bit of a show.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.81,0:20:44.23,Main,Head,0000,0000,0000,,W-We will offer you our loyalty!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.86,0:20:47.00,Main,Head,0000,0000,0000,,Please grant us your protection!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.00,0:20:51.06,Main,Head,0000,0000,0000,,If you do, we will swear our loyalty to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.06,0:20:52.24,Main,Leader,0000,0000,0000,,We will swear!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.19,0:20:55.99,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,This looks familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.99,0:20:59.23,Flashback,Tamura,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai! Just this once, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.23,0:21:01.24,Flashback,Mikami,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.76,0:21:05.79,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,When all is said and done, \NI just can't say no.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.28,0:21:13.21,Main,Goblin,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The Direwolves!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.21,0:21:15.06,Main,Goblin,0000,0000,0000,,This is terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.06,0:21:15.97,Main,Goblin,0000,0000,0000,,We're done for!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.18,0:21:18.47,Main,Goblin,0000,0000,0000,,We'll all be eaten!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.70,0:21:19.82,Main,Goblin,0000,0000,0000,,Let's run!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.82,0:21:21.30,Main,Goblin,0000,0000,0000,,B-But where?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.30,0:21:24.41,Main,Head,0000,0000,0000,,E-Everyone, please calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.41,0:21:26.10,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.98,0:21:29.73,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to defeat them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.60,0:21:31.98,Main,Head,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.96,0:21:43.30,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,In lieu of the Storm Dragon Veldora,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.30,0:21:46.25,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I, Rimuru Tempest, will grant your wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.30,0:21:51.05,Main,Head,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.05,0:21:56.13,Main,Head,0000,0000,0000,,We are your loyal servants, great Rimuru!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.52,0:21:57.89,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,You can count on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.16,0:22:02.57,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,And that's how I became the Goblins' leader,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.57,0:22:04.58,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,their guardian.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.66,0:23:39.78,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, "Battle at the Goblin Village."
